T1  - Short Selling on the New York Stock Exchange and the Effects of the Uptick Rule
AU  - Alexander, Gordon J.
AU  - Peterson, Mark A.
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 8
IS  - 1
SP  - 90
EP  - 116
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/01/01/
